profile:
Thank you for taking the time to visit our Homestars page!

We appreciate any opportunity to provide a free quote for your wet basement waterproofing and foundation crack repair. Dryshield is a Family owned and operated basement waterproofing company Toronto and most of southern Ontario. We pride ourselves on our basement waterproofing and foundation crack repair workmanship. Our mission is to continue providing you with the highest quality products, technologies and procedures at the most competitive price for your wet basement waterproofing needs.  We offer a wide range of solutions for your leaky or wet basement. Some of the solutions are; internal drainage systems, external waterproofing, window wells, basement crack repair and sump pumps.  

All of our work provided is Dryshield employed and not by subcontractors.  Our team at Dryshield works hard day in and day out to provide you with the highest quality of workmanship. 

We are fully licensed and insured. All prices are up front with no hidden surprises. Dryshield can beat any quality competitor with a difference in cost and quality.

Things to look for that can be contributing to your wet basement:

-	Are your down spouts discharging at the side of your house or are they connected to the ground?
-	Is the grade sloping towards your house causing a wet basement? 
-	Do you see any signs of a foundation concrete crack? 
-	How old is your home is and what condition are your weeping tiles are in?


If you have a wet basement and need a waterproofing company for your basement waterproofing needs contact Dryshield today!

www.waterproofingservice.com or 1-800-277-5411

profile:
Dry Space Waterproofing has been keeping water out of homes for over 20 years. We are fully licenced and insured company dedicated to providing the best and most affordable waterproofing services in GTA.
We offer a wide variety of home waterproofing services throughout the Greater Toronto Area. Our commitment is attention to details both large and small. We want to make you, the customer, totally satisfied through the whole construction process from the initial consultation to the final inspection. No job is too big or too small for us! 

We are committed to the employment of qualified, professional employees, building a reputation for quality workmanship. The employees on our staff are trained in the newest technologies and are encouraged to be actively involved in the advancement of knowledge within the company, ensuring that Dry Space Waterproofing Corp is always prepared for the fast-paced, quickly changing technologies of the future of the construction industry. We have access to the highest quality products and latest technology to help permanently repair your home. Customer Satisfaction is Our Goal! 

At Dry Space Waterproofing, we understand how important your home is to you, and treat your home like it was our own. Basements are an integral part of your whole house and cannot be ignored. Nobody wants a wet basement in the biggest investment of their life, and we are able to prevent that! If you've noticed leaks, standing water, or other waterproofing issues, call us today at 647- 671-5088 or contact us online to get an evaluation of your basement. Our experts will recommend the best solution for your needs. We offer FREE ESTIMATES on all our work.
